Comment: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,里維
Comment: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你別行動
Comment: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你很討厭送死吧
Comment: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是啊 很討厭
Comment: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,無論是去死還是讓人去死
Comment: 0,0:08:57.81,0:09:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,無法捨去任何東西的人
Comment: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就無法改變任何東西
Comment: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果需要凌駕怪物
Comment: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就連人性也可捨去
Comment: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我想亞妮她...
Comment: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就是做得到這點
Comment: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮...
Comment: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮!
Comment: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮...
Comment: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只有爸爸...
Comment: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,才是妳的夥伴
Comment: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我要...
Comment: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將巨人...
Comment: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給殺死...
Comment: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一隻不留地...
Comment: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個是!
Comment: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,住手!
Comment: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在還不清楚艾連能不能分辨出妳是誰
Comment: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那傢伙...
Comment: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,想要爬上...
Comment: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,牆壁是嗎?!
Comment: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不行了!
Comment: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣下去要讓她逃走了!
Comment: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,休想得逞!
Comment: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮...
Comment: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,下去吧
Comment: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮...
Comment: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是我錯了...
Comment: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,事到如今我已不再奢求妳的原諒
Comment: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是...
Comment: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只有一件事...
Comment: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我想拜託妳...
Comment: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,即便跟這世上的一切為敵也沒關係
Comment: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我要...
Comment: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將這世上全部的東西都給...
Comment: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,破壞殆盡!
Comment: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就算妳被整個世界...
Comment: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給怨恨著...
Comment: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只有爸爸...
Comment: 0,0:13:15.18,0:13:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,永遠是妳的夥伴
Comment: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,慘了!
Comment: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣裡面也要被吃掉了!
Comment: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連住手啊!
Comment: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我是...
Comment: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,自由的!
Comment: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以請妳答應我...
Comment: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要平安回來...
Comment: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,發生什麼事了?
Comment: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼了?
Comment: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,融化了!?
Comment: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎能把重要的證人給吃了
Comment: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,白癡
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,CM
Comment: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮呢...
Comment: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可惡...
Comment: 0,0:15:30.56,0:15:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,到底是怎樣啦!
Comment: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,都到這一步了 還什麼都不說嗎!
Comment: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮!
Comment: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我出來!
Comment: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,出來把事情做個了斷啊!
Comment: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂!太卑鄙了喔!
Comment: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮!
Comment: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮!!
Comment: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,住手
Comment: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒用的
Comment: 0,0:15:54.36,0:15:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,用繩索編個網子
Comment: 0,0:15:56.67,0:15:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,把這個綑起來送到地下去
Comment: 0,0:15:58.78,0:15:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,了解
Comment: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就一直這樣...
Comment: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,都沒從亞妮身上得到任何情報的話...
Comment: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那還剩下什麼...?
Comment: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,犧牲了這麼多人...
Comment: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,毀了他們的人生...
Comment: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,卻只留下一堆謎團...
Comment: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,又能怎麼樣呢...
Comment: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,說不上是作戰成功呢
Comment: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不
Comment: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們調查軍團的脖子已經接上了
Comment: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,恐怕只是脖子上的一片小皮而已
Comment: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果是這樣就好了
Comment: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾爾文
Comment: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,關於這次的作戰有幾個問題要問你
Comment: 0,0:16:56.97,0:16:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,既然已經知道目標是誰了
Comment: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼沒有找憲兵團來幫忙?
Comment: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,區長
Comment: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那是因為只要是女巨人的夥伴可能埋伏在附近的話
Comment: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們就必須用能夠證明自己是清白的人來執行任務
Comment: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是
Comment: 0,0:17:13.87,0:17:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為這樣史托黑斯區所受到的損害又要怎麼辦?
Comment: 0,0:17:17.94,0:17:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是我們實力不足所造成的
Comment: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我為我的粗心謝罪
Comment: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是道歉就能解決的事情嗎!
Comment: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果讓她繼續這樣下去的話
Comment: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,牆壁會被破壞
Comment: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,損害肯定會比現在還嚴重
Comment: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,原來如此
Comment: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,關於這次付出了巨大的損失的作戰
Comment: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有得到能阻止人類的滅亡的確切證據嗎?
Comment: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我是不覺得能從亞妮雷恩哈特身上得到
Comment: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是的 應該是不可能了
Comment: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也就是說...
Comment: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,完全是白白犧牲了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:17:59.20,0:17:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,身體還好嗎?
Comment: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯
Comment: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不舒服的感覺還是跟原本一樣
Comment: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮她...
Comment: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還是一樣硬化著呢
Comment: 0,0:18:23.81,0:18:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯
Comment: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,該死...
Comment: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,用了那麼大規模的作戰 結果卻連一點收穫都沒有嗎!
Comment: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也就是亞妮她守護情報到那種程度了
Comment: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯 被她順利地逃掉了
Comment: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,讓她逃掉的是艾連
Comment: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒錯吧 艾連
Comment: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果沒有那一瞬間的話
Comment: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是啊
Comment: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就跟阿爾敏說的一樣
Comment: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我失手了
Comment: 0,0:18:58.33,0:18:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看到亞妮之後
Comment: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我就下不了手了
Comment: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏．亞魯雷特
Comment: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,約翰．基爾休坦
Comment: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要來盤問事由了
Comment: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好的
Comment: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從我們兩個開始嗎?
Comment: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那就...回頭見
Comment: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個時候...
Comment: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我覺得很舒服
Comment: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,身體快壞掉了還覺得很清爽
Comment: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,覺得既然如此 就這樣...
Comment: 0,0:19:40.23,0:19:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,死了也沒關係
Comment: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在沒那樣想了啦
Comment: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你活著回來...
Comment: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真是太好了
Comment: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我沒辦法理解呢
Comment: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果要超越怪物的話
Comment: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就必須連人性也捨棄掉...
Comment: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不這樣的話贏不了嗎...
Comment: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是人類要贏過巨人的可能性之一
Comment: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我認為艾連做得到
Comment: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我說...即使變成那種怪物把巨人驅逐掉了...
Comment: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那還算是人類的勝利嗎?
Comment: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,吃吧
Comment: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒辦法...簡單地就超越...
Comment: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是
Comment: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我認為我抓住了讓人類生存下去的...
Comment: 0,0:21:15.40,0:21:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巨大的可能性
Comment: 0,0:21:21.02,0:21:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是還沒思考過人類能巨人化
Comment: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,抓住敵人的其中一人  是很大的進步
Comment: 0,0:21:30.53,0:21:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒錯
Comment: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那些傢伙一定還在
Comment: 0,0:21:33.97,0:21:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,讓我們把他們逼進絕路吧
Comment: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將那些在牆壁內的巨人們
Comment: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一個不剩地
Comment: 0,0:21:41.51,0:21:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這次該是我們進擊的時候了!
Comment: 0,0:21:48.52,0:21:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,調查軍團與艾連．葉卡召回王都的命令被凍結
Comment: 0,0:21:54.05,0:21:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,被收在地下深處的亞妮．雷恩哈特的管理
Comment: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,被交由調查軍團來負責
Comment: 0,0:22:02.62,0:22:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然而
Comment: 0,0:22:04.29,0:22:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類要知道自己被什麼東西給囚禁著的話
Comment: 0,0:22:11.02,0:22:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還需要更多的時間與犧牲
