Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.63,0:00:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.02,0:00:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這世界就是如此殘酷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我要...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}驅逐你們...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.14,0:00:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是殺光你們!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.54,0:00:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類回想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在他們支配之下的恐懼...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以及被囚禁在鳥籠之中的...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.26,0:00:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}屈辱...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.07,0:00:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}讓我們來祈禱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}羅塞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}席納
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}祈求三位女神依然健在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}祈禱大家的平安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}神聖的城牆不容許任何的質疑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}神之手親自打造的三道城牆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是因為我們的信仰之心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}才變得更加堅固
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}相信神明的純潔之心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}才是保護我們免於巨人危害的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也是唯一能擊退巨人的力量...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼會在這裡!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不可以...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.35,0:03:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不可以接近城牆...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}接近城牆...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這次似乎也保持住自己的意識了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連到目前為止一次也沒有贏過女巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他變成巨人了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他應該肚子非常餓的才對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:21.67,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}應該不會這麼簡單就...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}戰鬥... 並不是靠氣勢就能贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}約翰你應該也知道才對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要打倒那個亞妮...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要更加地...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是平地!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}女巨人要進入平地了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到那邊的話就無法進行立體機動!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}全部的人都向後撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}了解!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點 快點 快點啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}太奇怪了吧 為什麼巨人會...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳總是擺著一副大家都是白癡的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總是一臉感到很無趣的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但妳還是有充滿活力的時候...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就是妳在施展格鬥術的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然妳說學格鬥術一點意義都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.33,0:05:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但對我來說...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不認為妳心中是那麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳是個...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}很不會說謊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我一直以來都是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我說 亞妮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為了什麼而戰?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:06:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是因為什麼大義
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}才去殺人的!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}分隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算成功捕捉到女巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣下去城鎮會變成廢墟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}即便如此還是要做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是艾爾文下的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你也去做好捕捉的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我可沒聽過有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼這裡會有巨人在戰鬥?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.75,0:06:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到底...怎麼了...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你說巨人在互相戰鬥?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:06:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:07:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}城鎮損害到無法想像的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}居民與士兵出現了很多死傷者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾爾文!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這全部都是你的作戰所引發的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}全部都是我獨斷的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我沒打算狡辯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果在城鎮中實施這樣的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你應該知道事態會變成怎樣才是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼 你還能幹得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為了人類的...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你開什麼玩笑!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你這個反叛者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算我在此把你處刑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}想必上頭也不會說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}剩下來的指揮就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}蛤?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}絕對不要讓女巨人逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}隊伍展開是由佩魯擔當
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}補給是由拜依拉擔當
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}先去跟他們會合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.32,0:08:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再去東邊牆邊將女巨人給...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:02.76,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:03.63,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:04.60,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等等!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個...真的...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是為了人類才...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我相信這會成為那一大步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}全部的人把槍放下!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給他們上手銬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將所有的士兵全部派去現場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}優先完成居民的避難以及救援
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是的!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾爾文
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你的處刑就用正當的懲罰來解決
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等全部結束後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我很樂意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}里維
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你別行動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你很討厭送死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是啊 很討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}無論是去死還是讓人去死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:09:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}無法捨去任何東西的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就無法改變任何東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果需要凌駕怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就連人性也可捨去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我想亞妮她...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就是做得到這點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只有爸爸...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}才是妳的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我要...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將巨人...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給殺死...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一隻不留地...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個是!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在還不清楚艾連能不能分辨出妳是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}想要爬上...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}牆壁是嗎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不行了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣下去要讓她逃走了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}休想得逞!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是我錯了...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}事到如今我已不再奢求妳的原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只有一件事...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我想拜託妳...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}即便跟這世上的一切為敵也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我要...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將這世上全部的東西都給...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}破壞殆盡!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算妳被整個世界...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給怨恨著...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只有爸爸...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.18,0:13:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}永遠是妳的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}慘了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣裡面也要被吃掉了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連住手啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}自由的!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以請妳答應我...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要平安回來...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}發生什麼事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}融化了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎能把重要的證人給吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.56,0:15:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到底是怎樣啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}都到這一步了 還什麼都不說嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我出來!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}出來把事情做個了斷啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂!太卑鄙了喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.36,0:15:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}用繩索編個網子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.67,0:15:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把這個綑起來送到地下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.78,0:15:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就一直這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}都沒從亞妮身上得到任何情報的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那還剩下什麼...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}犧牲了這麼多人...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}毀了他們的人生...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}卻只留下一堆謎團...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}又能怎麼樣呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}說不上是作戰成功呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們調查軍團的脖子已經接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}恐怕只是脖子上的一片小皮而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果是這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾爾文
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}關於這次的作戰有幾個問題要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:16:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}既然已經知道目標是誰了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼沒有找憲兵團來幫忙?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}區長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那是因為只要是女巨人的夥伴可能埋伏在附近的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們就必須用能夠證明自己是清白的人來執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.87,0:17:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為這樣史托黑斯區所受到的損害又要怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.94,0:17:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是我們實力不足所造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我為我的粗心謝罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是道歉就能解決的事情嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果讓她繼續這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}牆壁會被破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}損害肯定會比現在還嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}關於這次付出了巨大的損失的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有得到能阻止人類的滅亡的確切證據嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我是不覺得能從亞妮雷恩哈特身上得到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是的 應該是不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也就是說...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}完全是白白犧牲了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:17:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}身體還好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不舒服的感覺還是跟原本一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮她...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還是一樣硬化著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.81,0:18:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}該死...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}用了那麼大規模的作戰 結果卻連一點收穫都沒有嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也就是亞妮她守護情報到那種程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗯 被她順利地逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}讓她逃掉的是艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒錯吧 艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果沒有那一瞬間的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就跟阿爾敏說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我失手了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:18:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}看到亞妮之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我就下不了手了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏．亞魯雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}約翰．基爾休坦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要來盤問事由了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從我們兩個開始嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那就...回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個時候...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我覺得很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}身體快壞掉了還覺得很清爽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}覺得既然如此 就這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.23,0:19:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}死了也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在沒那樣想了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你活著回來...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我沒辦法理解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果要超越怪物的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就必須連人性也捨棄掉...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不這樣的話贏不了嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是人類要贏過巨人的可能性之一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我認為艾連做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我說...即使變成那種怪物把巨人驅逐掉了...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那還算是人類的勝利嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒辦法...簡單地就超越...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我認為我抓住了讓人類生存下去的...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.40,0:21:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨大的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.02,0:21:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是還沒思考過人類能巨人化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}抓住敵人的其中一人  是很大的進步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.53,0:21:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那些傢伙一定還在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.97,0:21:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}讓我們把他們逼進絕路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將那些在牆壁內的巨人們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一個不剩地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.51,0:21:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這次該是我們進擊的時候了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.52,0:21:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}調查軍團與艾連．葉卡召回王都的命令被凍結
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.05,0:21:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}被收在地下深處的亞妮．雷恩哈特的管理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}被交由調查軍團來負責
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.62,0:22:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}然而
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.29,0:22:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類要知道自己被什麼東西給囚禁著的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.02,0:22:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還需要更多的時間與犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.96,0:22:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}
